{"parentUuid":"919cd58c-ab3b-4121-8324-9bbac8b13554","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01SyxuVnAYvDFdXZzN2TG7FP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Before I build this, two quick clarifications:\n\n1. **Submission target** — is this UI-only (the \"Create\" button just closes the modal with a toast/confirmation, maybe logs the payload to console), or do you want a mock `/api/jira` endpoint that echoes back a fake ticket key like `UX-1234`? For a trial demo, mock-only is usually enough but the fake endpoint adds a little more authenticity if you want to show network calls.\n\n2. **Prefill mapping** — here's what I'd default to (editable in the modal):\n   - **Summary**: first sentence of the issue description, truncated to ~80 chars\n   - **Issue Type**: `Bug` (genuine_bug) / `Task` (stylistic_choice) / `Spike` (needs_investigation)\n   - **Priority**: `Highest` (critical) / `High` (major) / `Medium` (minor)\n   - **Labels**: the category (e.g., `navigation`, `accessibility`)\n   - **Description**: formatted block with the issue, critic reasoning, timestamp (as a \"Reproduce at 1:23\" line), and verdict\n   - **Reporter**: \"UX Analyzer Bot\" (placeholder)\n   - **Assignee**: empty (unassigned)\n\n   Sound right, or would you change any of that?\n\nAnd my plan for the button placement: only on `ValidatedCard` (skeletons don't have a verdict yet), small \"Create Ticket\" link-button in the card footer next to the timestamp. Modal opens with the prefilled form, has the Jira breadcrumb + icon in the header you described, Summary/Type/Priority/Labels/Description fields (all editable), Cancel + Create buttons. ESC and backdrop click close it."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":123059,"cache_read_input_tokens":14792,"output_tokens":1552,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":123059,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":1552,"cache_read_input_tokens":14792,"cache_creation_input_tokens":123059,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":123059},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaP4457bJPBAHCiwJctxV","type":"assistant","uuid":"bfb14f41-bdcf-48d0-b38e-84bc141e6e87","timestamp":"2026-04-24T18:16:41.387Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/home/akshay/projects/video_ux_analyzer","sessionId":"43aa6f4e-238a-49ff-bcee-676bf9b5ead2","version":"2.1.118","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
